Package: vigiar
Type: Package
Title: Download Data from Brazil's VIGIAR Power BI Dashboard
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ryan", "Santos", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "santosry@protonmail.com"),
    person("vigiar", "team", role = "ctb"))
Description: Provides functions to download air quality (PM2.5),
    population exposure, and health surveillance data from Brazil's
    VIGIAR (Vigilância em Saúde Ambiental) Power BI dashboard,
    maintained by the Brazilian Ministry of Health. The package
    handles Power BI session management, API authentication,
    automatic decompression of the DSR (Data Shape Response) format,
    and returns tidy data frames ready for analysis.
